Hey, how it possible that campaign with 200 daily budget spend more than 800?

Hey there! It sounds like your campaign might be using a bidding strategy that optimizes for conversions, such as Maximize Conversions. This strategy can sometimes exceed the daily budget to maximize the number of conversions. If you want more control over your spending, you might consider switching to a CPC or CPM model. For more details on how these strategies work, check out this article: [Introduction to Maximize Conversions](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20624355375117-Introduction-to-Maximize-Conversions). Let me know if you have any other questions!

Got it! For a newsletter campaign, it's unusual for the spend to exceed the set daily budget. It might be worth checking if there were any changes in your campaign settings or if there was a temporary glitch. If everything seems correct on your end, I recommend reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance. They can look into this issue more deeply for you.
